### Profiles API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/profiles
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here
@profileId = replace_with_actual_profile_id

### 1. Create tone/style profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Brand Voice - Bold & Modern",
  "description": "Our signature style for all content",
  "isDefault": true,
  "image": {
    "style": "modern",
    "mood": ["professional", "energetic", "innovative"],
    "colorPalette": {
      "primary": ["#0066FF", "#00CCFF"],
      "secondary": ["#FF00FF", "#FFFF00"]
    },
    "lighting": "dramatic",
    "composition": "rule-of-thirds"
  },
  "video": {
    "pacing": "fast",
    "energy": "high",
    "transitions": ["cut", "zoom", "swipe"],
    "musicStyle": ["electronic", "upbeat"],
    "colorGrading": "vibrant"
  },
  "voice": {
    "pace": "moderate",
    "emotion": "enthusiastic",
    "personality": "confident",
    "pitch": "medium",
    "accent": "neutral"
  },
  "article": {
    "writingStyle": "conversational",
    "formality": "informal",
    "vocabulary": "moderate",
    "sentenceLength": "medium",
    "readingLevel": "8th-grade"
  }
}

### 2. List profiles
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles?contentType=image&isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get profile by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/{{profileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profiles/{{profileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated brand voice with more energy",
  "video": {
    "pacing": "very-fast",
    "energy": "very-high"
  }
}

### 5. Delete profile
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/profiles/{{profileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Apply profile to prompt (THE MAGIC!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/{{profileId}}/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Create a product launch video",
  "contentType": "video"
}

### 7. Analyze tone compliance
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/{{profileId}}/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hey everyone! Check out our AMAZING new product! It's literally going to blow your mind! 🤯",
  "contentType": "caption"
}

### 8. Get default profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/default?contentType=video
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Generate profile from examples
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Auto-Generated Brand Voice",
  "description": "Generated from past successful content",
  "examples": [
    "Behind the scenes of our product development! 🚀",
    "Here's how we build innovative solutions that save you time.",
    "Pro tip: Always test before you ship! Quality matters."
  ],
  "contentType": "caption"
}


